        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Si sacris et venerabilibus locis temporalia et transitoria
                        impendimus, eterna et sine fine mansura nos auxiliante Domino adipisci
                        nequaquam difidimus. Quapropter omnium [fidelium] sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet et futurorum noverit industria, <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Adalardus">Adelardum</name></persName>
                        illustrem <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionem</rs> dilectissimum <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fidelem nostrum</rs> nostram suppliciter exorasse
                        clementiam, quatenus <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/211">sancti Iohannis</orgName>
                        intra hanc <placeName ref="#places/65">Ticinensem civitatem</placeName>
                        fundate dignaremur concedere, confirmare et corroborare sub plenissima
                        integritate omnes res et possessiones quas ipsa ecclesia Sancti Iohannis tam
                        per donum sanctae memorie <persName key="#Queen" ref="#people/299"
                            >Gondiperge</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">reginae</rs>, que ipsam edificavit ecclesiam, quam per
                        precepta regum et imperatorum seu et firmitates aliorum religiosorum hominum
                        actenus habere et detinere dinoscitur. Cuius precibus aclinati, ita fieri
                        anuimus, huius nostre concessionis et confirmationis preceptum scribi
                        iubentes, [per quod] prenominate ecclesie Sancti Iohannis concedimus,
                        confirmamus et sub omni integritate coroboramus omnes res et possessiones
                        suas quas priscis temporibus tenuit et possedit, eo videlicet ordine, ut
                        ipsa ecclesia omnes res et possessiones suas, quas sibi per donum
                        prenominate regine et per precepta antecessorum nostrorum regum videlicet et
                        imperatorum et firmitates aliorum bonorum hominum possidere cernitur,
                        deinceps per hoc nostrum preceptum cum omni sua integritate teneat et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pleniter possideat</rs>, tam eas res et possessiones que ad partem
                        publicam regni nostri pertinuerunt quam et illas quas nostri antecessores,
                        reges videlicet et imperatores per sua precepta ob amorem Dei et sancti
                        Iohannis <rs key="#Monks">canonicis</rs> in ipsa ecclesia Deo militantibus
                        ad victum et vestimentum specialiter tribuerunt et denominative
                        concesserunt, videlicet infra menia huius Ticinensis [civitatis] <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >capellam</rs> unam <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Sancti Victoris</orgName> constructam cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >solario ante se et solariolum unum</rs> post tribunal prope <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes" ref="#estates/304">cortem Palatiolum</geogName>,
                            <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansiones duas</rs> penes <geogName key="#Houses #Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/305">cortem Genuensem</geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >salatiolum unum</rs> ante portam eiusdem ecclesie, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansiones duas</rs>, claustra in circuitu ecclesie cum viridatio extra
                        muros civitatis, <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >hortulos duos</rs> prope basilicam Sancti Victoris, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >clausuram unam</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >campos tres</rs>, infra menia ipsius civitatis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >braidam unam</rs>, in <placeName>Nassaria</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pratellos quinque</rs>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName>Terra
                            Arsa</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >pratum unum</rs> simul cum <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >silvula</rs>, in <placeName>Monteferrato</placeName> in loco qui
                        dicitur <placeName>Rivassi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos quinque</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Islands #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >insula infra Padum</rs>, <placeName>in Altruelini</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, <placeName>in Bertesassi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, <placeName>in Pulveria</placeName><rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            > mansum unum</rs>, <placeName>in Bucellade</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansum unum</rs>, <placeName>in Gebedi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansum unum</rs>, in loco qui nuncupatur
                            <placeName>Archidiaconi</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos septem</rs>, <placeName>in Balbiano</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem unum</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Fundi #Landed_possessions" ref="#places/43">civitate
                            Placentina</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >salatiolam unam</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Fundi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >parvo horto</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >campo uno</rs>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName>Sancti
                            Cipriani</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >capellam unam</rs> cum domo coltili et <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >mansos quatuor</rs> et cum omni sua pertinentia, <placeName>in
                            Segestri</placeName> quandam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >absentem terram</rs>, similiter <placeName>in Levarnia</placeName> et
                            <placeName>in Caurani</placeName> ac infra civitatem <placeName
                            ref="#places/626">Genuesam</placeName> et in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/306">comitatu Terdonensi</geogName>, similiter in loco ubi
                        dicitur <placeName>Regiana</placeName>, <placeName>Mariana</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Verlasca</placeName>, <placeName>Freneto</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Cassiano</placeName>, nec non et
                            <placeName>Topiole</placeName>, in <geogName key="#Comitatus">comitatu
                            Aquensi</geogName> in loco ubi dicitur <placeName>Cuspiano</placeName>
                        cum omni sua integritate, in <placeName>Cavanasco</placeName> mansos tres et
                        absentem unum, in <placeName>Frisosco</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Bibiano</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Miolaco</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Gambaro</placeName> mansos duos cum <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >molendino</rs>, in <placeName>Moliana</placeName> manentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Corliasco</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Merlade</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Visedano</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Carponio</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Frontinassi</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Grameneto</placeName> absentem unum, in
                            <placeName>Turredano</placeName> mansum unum, in
                            <placeName>Aurello</placeName> petias de <rs key="#Wine">vitibus</rs>
                        duas et campellum unum, <geogName key="#Curtes">cortem de
                            Robationico</geogName> cum omnibus pertinentiis suis et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Royal_slave"
                            >familiis utriusque sexus</rs> et districtionibus, in
                            <placeName>Carvina</placeName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Royal_aldius"
                            >aldiones</rs> reddentes ceram ad luminaria prefate ecclesie, similiter
                        in <placeName>Pino</placeName> et in <placeName>Canobio</placeName>, hec
                        solumodo usui et utilitati canonicorum pretaxate ecclesie que nuncupatur
                        Domnarum, sicut alii nostri antecessores reges et imperatores per sua
                        precepta et alii religiosi et sancti viri per suas firmitates concesserunt,
                        in et nos per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus, confirmamus et pleniter
                        coroboramus et perdonamus, ea videlicet ratione, ut tam <persName
                            key="#Archpriests"><name ref="Agibertus">Agevertus</name></persName>
                        ipsius ecclesie <rs key="#Archpriests">archipresbiter</rs> et prepositus
                        sibique subditi canonici quam et eorum successores qui ibi pro tempore
                        fuerint hec per huius nostre auctoritatis donativum teneant ac possideant et
                        exinde integram potestatem habeant faciendi quicquid voluerint more
                        ceterorum canonicorum, quatenus in nostra mercede Deo et sancto Iohanni
                        securi valeant deservire. Et si ipse archipresbiter et prepositus vel
                        successores eiusdem ecclesie ab hac luce migraverit, non aliunde sed ex sinu
                        ispius ecclesie sibi archipresbiterum et prepositum eligant. Reliqua omnia
                        ad eandem ecclesiam pertinentia pars publica regni nostri per hoc nostrum
                        pracmaticum pleniter teneat et cum omni integritate possideat, sua omnium
                        hominum inquietudine et contradictione remota. Si quis igitur huius nostre
                        concessionis et confirmationis preceptum infringere vel violare aliquando
                        presumpserit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras
                            ducentum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere palatii
                            nostri</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            parti ipsius ecclesie Sancti Iohannis</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo
                        nostro subter iussimus insigniri. Signum (M) domni Berengarii gloriosissimi
                        regis. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data non. Kal. Iul.,
                        anno dominice incarnationis DCCCCVIIII, anno vero domni Berengarii
                        gloriosissimi regis XXII, indictione duodecima, Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName> palatii. In Christi nomine feliciter,
                        amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
